QuestData.Title: Stranger in an Even Stranger Land
QuestData.Description:
<You arrive alone at the precipice of a strange city, knowing the leaders of Azeroth remain trapped in the Maw.
Wherever you are, it is clearly very, very far from home.
It appears your arrival has been noticed.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Find your way inside Oribos to learn what is happening.
QuestData.RewardText: Could it be? An actual mortal being in the Eternal City? The Purpose be served!
